<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="severe-adj">severe <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /sɪ'vɪə(r)/    美 /sɪ'vɪr/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>严重的</strong></h4>
<p>extremely bad or serious：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>severe damage / a severe crisis 
严重的损害/危机</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>严厉的；苛刻的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>be severe with oneself
严于律己</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>严峻的；激烈的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the severe winter
严冬</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>severe competition
激烈的竞争</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>severely /sə'vɪrlɪ/ adv   </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a severely polluted lake
严重污染的湖</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Anyone breaking the law will be severely punished.
任何人犯法都会受到严惩。</p></div></div>